Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.28,0:00:04.60,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}安潔莉娜·菜夏·史威爾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.38,0:00:09.60,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然很不器用 還請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.10,0:00:16.75,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有什麼事請儘管吩咐 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.81,0:00:20.09,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就算你突然這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.99,0:00:22.74,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}櫻乃 你有什麼需要做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:24.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒什麼特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.64,0:00:29.50,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 打掃房間洗衣服什麼都可以 請儘管吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.05,0:00:35.81,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}洗完的衣服已經疊好了 房間都被哥哥認真打掃過了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.21,0:00:37.59,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是主人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.03,0:00:39.40,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.70,0:00:41.22,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.84,0:00:44.78,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那我來做飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.34,0:00:48.35,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}做飯是我的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.78,0:00:50.10,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.27,0:00:54.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}安潔從孩童時期開始 一直在磨練女僕的技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.87,0:00:58.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一定能做出讓主人滿意的飯菜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.64,0:01:03.05,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那樣的話 就讓我見識一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.19,0:01:04.87,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}能讓我做了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.54,0:01:10.07,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也做 然後讓哥哥進行評價
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.39,0:01:11.03,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.48,0:01:14.59,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}原來如此 就是料理對決啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.50,0:01:17.23,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}請多多關照

Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.38,0:02:52.57,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\pos(1095,580)}{\pos(980,560)}{\3c&HB58E00&}{\fn方正综艺_GBK\fs40\fad(500,300)}探索的洗澡時間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.83,0:02:53.73,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.58,0:02:56.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}請盡情享用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.36,0:03:03.28,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我開始吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:12.50,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}吃太多了 而且哪邊還都不能剩下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.19,0:03:17.18,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}主人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.29,0:03:25.26,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我來給您擦背
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.61,0:03:26.88,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}來吧 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.12,0:03:30.16,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等 等…一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.71,0:03:31.22,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.93,0:03:32.47,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:34.61,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.88,0:03:49.24,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哥哥 沒睡好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.57,0:03:51.28,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.44,0:03:55.53,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那之後也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.81,0:04:00.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}上完洗手間 拿著擦手巾在門口等我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.95,0:04:03.56,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說要幫我刷牙 到處追著我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.57,0:04:07.93,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}最後還說要陪我睡 追到了床上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.88,0:04:17.34,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}能和主人一起上學 安潔真的是太幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.62,0:04:24.09,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嘛 看她那麼高興就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.92,0:04:32.64,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}歡迎回來 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.23,0:04:33.86,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.03,0:04:36.47,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 那不很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.87,0:04:40.19,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}安潔 我們可是一起上學來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.59,0:04:46.50,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}果然要是不在這裡說這句話 就總覺得缺少點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.91,0:04:51.21,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 在家和在這都這麼說 總覺得有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.78,0:04:54.32,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別一大早就別這裡說相聲了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:04:57.07,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 早上好 瀨名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.04,0:04:59.74,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.04,0:05:17.34,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}櫻乃 安潔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.09,0:05:18.65,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:21.26,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我稍微離開一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:22.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}主人?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.47,0:05:31.50,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我馬上就餵你吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.95,0:05:36.96,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瓜生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.38,0:05:39.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早上好 天羽前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:43.22,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早上好 發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.61,0:05:43.07,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}鴿子的飼料
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.61,0:05:43.07,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Mix Food P
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.51,0:05:46.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒什麼 剛才看到了前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:48.03,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.77,0:05:50.25,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是大家的早飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.78,0:05:54.60,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.94,0:05:59.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}小熊喵 再稍等一會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.51,0:05:58.94,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美味增加
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.39,0:06:01.32,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個 我來幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.58,0:06:02.10,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.64,0:06:05.95,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那 就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.26,0:06:14.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好吃嗎 小熊喵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:21.96,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}前輩 你真是的喜歡動物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.62,0:06:23.14,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.05,0:06:29.65,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.51,0:06:31.27,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.75,0:06:36.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}讓我 讓我加入喵咪部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.52,0:06:42.28,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了 突然間這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.71,0:06:48.89,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起 我聽到你和學園長說關於廢部的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:52.80,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.43,0:06:56.64,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不過 但不僅僅是這個理由
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.70,0:07:00.53,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我想要幫助前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.84,0:07:02.63,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.54,0:07:06.60,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.29,0:07:09.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我非常高興
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.85,0:07:12.34,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:16.67,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}歡迎來到喵咪部 瓜生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.73,0:07:18.45,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:21.06,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起 我來晚…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.38,0:07:26.15,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你這傢伙 你這垃圾蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.56,0:07:29.79,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼會和美羽前輩兩個人獨處的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.37,0:07:31.01,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.29,0:07:32.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}到底什麼不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:35.87,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}來得正好 小紗凪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.25,0:07:38.28,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有什麼事嗎 美羽前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:41.96,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天開始瓜生也是我們社團的一員了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:43.19,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.14,0:07:46.06,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.99,0:07:56.67,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 你加入喵咪部了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.11,0:07:59.40,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 我好像沒說過...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.92,0:08:01.23,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天早上才加入的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.60,0:08:05.84,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}本想著今天不用去學生會 能和你一起回家的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.07,0:08:09.47,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起了 等會必須去社團
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.52,0:08:10.64,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.92,0:08:21.28,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要在學園內張貼這個 過來幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.86,0:08:24.69,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵咪部部員募集!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.59,0:08:26.04,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}部員募集
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.71,0:08:30.46,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你認可我是部員了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.99,0:08:34.75,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那也沒辦法 美羽前輩都批准了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.31,0:08:38.47,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}作為交換 你要給我好好幹活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.09,0:08:40.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好的 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.19,0:08:45.82,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 有保護狐狸嗎

Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.12,0:08:59.60,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個 全部是你一個人畫的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.20,0:09:02.72,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真對不起了 畫得不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.00,0:09:04.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 不是說這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.04,0:09:07.08,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:13.43,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒什麼大不了的 只要是為了喵咪部…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.79,0:09:20.64,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.42,0:09:30.40,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只要是為了美羽前輩 這點小事…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.46,0:09:30.50,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}喵咪部部員募集!!\N喜歡動物的人\N對動物有責任心的人\N不一起來幫助讓受傷的動物回歸自然嗎?\N詳細請到喵咪部

Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.91,0:09:36.23,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}歡迎回來 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.11,0:09:40.12,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天的晚餐是煎肉餅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.48,0:09:41.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天也努力做了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.28,0:09:42.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.32,0:09:46.86,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}難道說 又是對決嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.28,0:09:52.06,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 我不會再做讓主人難受的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.53,0:09:55.17,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}安潔和我都反省了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.57,0:09:59.40,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}於是 這次合作做的菜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.06,0:10:04.32,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喔 看起來很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.43,0:10:07.33,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好 快來吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.25,0:10:08.79,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.38,0:10:09.87,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.51,0:10:14.65,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.47,0:10:16.49,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.41,0:10:18.75,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學園長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.15,0:10:21.63,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我來接安潔了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.00,0:10:22.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.02,0:10:27.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}和安潔的媽媽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.97,0:10:30.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的 很早以前就認識了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.93,0:10:35.57,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}她給一個人留在日本的安潔訂下了一個條件
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.22,0:10:38.53,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不會說 你忘記了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.73,0:10:39.49,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}安潔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.06,0:10:46.17,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}住在結女 給學園幫忙的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.73,0:10:50.14,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也就是說 在這裡住著…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.61,0:10:53.65,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}打破了那個約定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.06,0:10:59.73,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}噢… 好不容易才找到了主人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.25,0:11:02.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}估計你沒有難過的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:03.86,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.31,0:11:06.27,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個 在合校之際
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.43,0:11:10.18,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學園的事務工作 增加了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.53,0:11:13.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}而你卻不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.56,0:11:15.76,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學生會長都發出哀鳴了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.18,0:11:21.53,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}安潔 被需要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.00,0:11:25.98,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的 說是希望你盡早回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.99,0:11:31.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這句話 作為女僕不能不管
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.22,0:11:34.67,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}主人 雖然很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.73,0:11:36.35,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但安潔不能不去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.97,0:11:39.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 看起來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.96,0:11:41.89,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}安潔都興奮起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.32,0:11:44.75,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學園長 快點回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.75,0:11:49.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 真冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:52.78,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天突然變得好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.87,0:11:56.35,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個秋天最強的一次降溫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:12:00.49,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個季節 第一次戴圍巾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.02,0:12:08.37,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}歡迎回來 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:10.13,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}-我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:10.13,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}-我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.01,0:12:13.02,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}果然這樣更習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.36,0:12:15.16,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要習慣 我就該煩惱了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.97,0:12:17.80,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}安潔可沒有放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.32,0:12:23.45,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}總有一天 會回到主人家去工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.00,0:12:25.74,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.76,0:12:31.37,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.80,0:12:34.04,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早上好瀨名 乾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:39.20,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}看起來 好像有事發生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.18,0:12:42.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 海報…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.99,0:12:44.18,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.17,0:12:46.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一定是學生會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.73,0:12:47.23,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:48.34,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:50.70,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 新吾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.39,0:13:00.49,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起 請等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.60,0:13:01.14,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.71,0:13:04.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.99,0:13:07.41,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在做什麼 新吾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.71,0:13:29.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.47,0:13:34.50,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 照顧動物習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.55,0:13:35.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.84,0:13:41.08,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}剩下的只有兩份啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:43.60,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.86,0:13:45.96,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}又不是你該道歉的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.46,0:13:48.79,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}做到這個份上 你是笨蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.98,0:13:51.51,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.03,0:13:57.93,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.58,0:14:02.63,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個學校的校規
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.45,0:14:09.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要被認可為正式的社團 需要顧問和六個部員
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.03,0:14:11.85,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}顧問已經有著落了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.29,0:14:17.16,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 部員只有美羽前輩 我和垃圾蟲而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.03,0:14:19.47,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以去張貼海報的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.77,0:14:23.67,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 為什麼不能得到學生會的許可呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.93,0:14:26.23,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣的內容 只要去申請…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.29,0:14:27.95,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果有時間 早就這麼做了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.90,0:14:32.63,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是… 決定廢部的教師會議就是明天了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.61,0:14:38.34,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在那之前 如果不再湊齊三個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.22,0:14:41.32,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喵咪部就…

Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.91,0:14:49.38,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒關係的 我們不是在吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:55.38,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個海報 可以拿走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:56.93,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.48,0:14:59.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可以是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.03,0:15:02.40,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個孩子是小熊喵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.09,0:15:06.15,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你可真能看出來啊 僅憑這樣的畫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:07.43,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:10.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}畫得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.57,0:15:14.67,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我覺得畫中充滿了感情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.47,0:15:21.49,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哥哥 我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.87,0:15:27.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}前輩 確定了兩名新入部員
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.63,0:15:28.22,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.79,0:15:29.77,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:30.79,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.34,0:15:33.09,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天開始請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.77,0:15:35.78,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.81,0:15:38.11,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣就5個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.43,0:15:39.94,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒

Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.69,0:15:47.40,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 紗凪 快救救我

Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.99,0:15:48.44,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別再追我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:51.95,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瀨名看起來沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.79,0:15:51.84,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.26,0:15:53.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}新吾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.43,0:16:00.15,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我知道 你很忙嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.22,0:16:02.10,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:07.11,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還有一個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.18,0:16:11.63,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一定要想點辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.71,0:16:13.19,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.04,0:16:21.77,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那我回學生會 取得張貼海報的許可
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.20,0:16:23.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.21,0:16:26.98,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}工作就中午開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:29.49,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.82,0:16:33.71,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}其它的工作我會盡快做完 然後就來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.57,0:16:36.72,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只要在放學前貼出海報
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.91,0:16:38.67,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就能讓回去的學生看到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.15,0:16:40.28,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣一個人應該…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.36,0:16:41.87,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}給我等等 垃圾蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.84,0:16:44.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼一個人就擅自決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.43,0:16:49.21,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒關係的 還要請乾畫小熊喵的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.84,0:16:51.22,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣不是很好嗎 小紗凪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.71,0:16:54.41,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這裡就拜託瓜生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.31,0:16:58.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯… 美羽前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.52,0:17:40.51,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你那邊怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.72,0:17:42.48,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.11,0:17:46.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣就完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.77,0:17:58.22,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}會有人來嗎 新入部員
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:23.35,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒辦法了 雨越來越大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.74,0:18:25.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:30.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要來我家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.55,0:18:32.15,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.53,0:18:35.71,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}從這裡的話 我家會近很多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.99,0:18:38.74,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我借給你雨傘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.03,0:18:40.80,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.10,0:18:44.09,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等等 你要…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.75,0:18:48.64,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣比較不會淋濕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.20,0:18:54.06,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.08,0:19:02.97,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:04.14,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.86,0:19:07.65,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還有 雨傘在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.18,0:19:12.49,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}現在再借雨傘 也沒什麼意義了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.45,0:19:13.98,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.07,0:19:19.70,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}先去洗個澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.96,0:19:20.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.10,0:19:24.74,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你是因為借給我外套 才淋得那麼濕的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.47,0:19:26.38,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.64,0:19:31.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瀨名才是 快點洗澡好些
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.06,0:19:34.76,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}腿都凍得發抖了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.77,0:19:38.83,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我沒事的 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.12,0:19:40.27,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瓜生去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.65,0:19:42.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不去 我就不讓你回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.86,0:19:46.10,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.75,0:19:49.08,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是瀨名先去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.30,0:19:49.87,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.18,0:19:53.18,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是瓜生不先去洗澡的話 我就不去洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:56.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那樣變得是我為難了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.89,0:20:00.75,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是你感冒了 我也會為難的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.98,0:20:11.15,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是這樣下去 兩個人都會感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.67,0:20:23.20,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.19,0:20:40.43,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}轉那個方向過去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.47,0:20:42.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊… 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.73,0:21:02.80,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼不邀請我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.50,0:21:03.93,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.84,0:21:05.67,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喵咪部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.05,0:21:07.84,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.98,0:21:10.32,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是還差一個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.86,0:21:15.29,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瀨名不是不擅長和動物打交道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.14,0:21:18.85,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.37,0:21:23.25,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就算再怎麼想幫社團 也不能邀請瀨名
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.49,0:21:28.46,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.26,0:21:45.38,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你就是這樣的傢伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.58,0:21:55.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我 要加入喵咪部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.22,0:23:29.66,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美羽 在那發現了鱷魚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.94,0:23:31.40,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}讓喵咪部保護它吧
